{{WsBox
|name=Progression 
|desc=[{{wsSize}}] boost to [element] allies' [element] ATK based on number of turns passed
|aura_boostable=yes
|color=red
|boost1=E. ATK (Prog.)
}}
* Boost to Elemental ATK by a given amount per turn. Each skill instance comes with its individual maximum amount.
* Both Elemental ATK per turn and individual maximum are boosted by auras.
* Elemental ATK from Progression skills caps at 75% total.
* When using multiple Progression skills, the 75% cap can be reached before each skill reaches its individual maximum.
* Despite the similarities, {{ItmGSI|header=Draconic Weapons:|title=Draconic Weapons|Draconic Harp|Draconic Buster|Draconic Bow|Draconic Rod|Draconic Blade|Draconic Fire}} boost EX ATK and do not count towards the Progression skill cap.
